{
  "name": "Wind Release Multilayered Gale",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Wind.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You wave your hands back and forth creating layers of wind that stack on top of one another creating a barrier of wind. Your Wall of wind is extremely dense not allowing most things to pass through it. When you create your barrier of wind it has 30 Hit points. It occupies your space with you and protects you in all direction, ranged attacks targeting you are made at disadvantage. At the start of each of your turns you can enhance this barrier regenerating 3d6 of the barriers hit points. This Barrier has a vulnerability to Fire damage, and resistance to Lightning damage.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the initial hit points of the barrier by 10.</p>",
